{"tid":2252564,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"輕鬆扮識煮飯系列-蒜香紙包骨","createTime":"2020-10-21T14:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T11:03:29.000Z","uid":68594,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0f2529b3374de4076bdc65e8fefa3ef8c175d51e","tid":2252564,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:15:50.000Z","msg":"大家好！我係子言張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日教大家整一啲「好似識煮飯嘅嘢」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時冇煮飯嘅朋友應該都係煎下腸仔加隻蛋，有朋友嚟食飯都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣今次就幫到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個製作簡單！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nu6ySkQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnu6ySkQ.jpg&h=dec18f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煎好晒之後放入焗爐就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出嚟個賣相仲幾靚添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pVD9UjHxArY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpVD9UjHxArY&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=c82d30af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pVD9UjHxArY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5mGgNJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5mGgNJ.png&h=25282e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🔴材料<br />\n五花腩排........200克<br />\n蒜頭............1個<br />\n蔥..............1紥<br />\n唐芹............1紥<br />\n乾蔥頭..........2粒<br />\n莞茜............1紥<br />\n<br />\n🔴調味料<br />\n生抽、紹興酒、麻油、炸蒜粒、鹽、糖、雞粉、生粉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🔴步驟：<br />\n1.五花腩排切成約2cm厚度的小塊<br />\n2.倒入調味料：半蓋紹興酒、兩至三圈生抽、兩至三圈麻油、兩匙生粉、半匙雞粉<br />\n3.撈勻後用保鮮紙包好放進雪櫃冷藏30分鐘或以上<br />\n4.蔥切走尾部，然後切成蔥花、唐芹沖洗乾淨後把莖的部分切碎<br />\n5.蒜頭去皮、乾蔥對半切開及去皮，一同放入攪拌機攪碎，然後倒進蔥及唐芹內<br />\n6.冷鑊落油，油熱後倒入醃好的腩排<br />\n7.腩排兩面煎至金黃色後先上夾起備用，無需煎至熟透<br />\n8.準備錫紙，每張大約A5大小<br />\n9.把煎好的腩排及一至兩茶匙蒜香放到錫紙中間，然後包好<br />\n10.焗爐180度預熱15分鐘，把蒜香骨放入焗爐焗25分鐘<br />\n11.取出蒜香骨試味<br />\n<br />\n最後鍾意我呢段片嘅朋友可以俾個like我啦或者可以訂閱我嘅Channel嘅！我哋下一段片再見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n►Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheung.newhandcooking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheung.newhandcooking&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=c7bde1cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheung.newhandcooking</a><br />\n►訂閱我：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/子言張\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2F%E5%AD%90%E8%A8%80%E5%BC%B5&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=16c3f178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/c/子言張</a>"},{"pid":"24514854ad43a22fcf9db1b850774d4e8b66af3c","tid":2252564,"uid":93141,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"點解好似好濕，應該要乾身脆口同啡啡地少燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5b96359509b06367efd3e460e4d4e1edea1185","tid":2252564,"uid":279333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff775a433e4fe4ca3483847e9b4722551e408cf4","tid":2252564,"uid":54623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T14:26:46.000Z","msg":"一路幫